Features to Implement:

1. Notification replacement for oil, brakes, wheels, wheel aligment, rotating tires, battery, ac filter. For each of these, put a bar that fills up indicating how much time is left before notification appears.

2. Line graph of MPG, Miles, Gallons, and Cost using date of gas refill as the x-axis. Allow graphs to be plotted separately or together. Compare month to month or year to year.

3. Add number of days driven on each tank of gas.

4. Add white icons for gas, miles, gallons